SHE is one of the brilliant women who bestrode the Nigerian corporate sector. A former head of operations of UBA Prestige Bank and a former general manager, South West, MTN Nigeria, Funmi is a successful career woman in all ramifications. A recurring decimal on the social scene, she not only took pride in gracing most red carpet events, she repeatedly made the cover of many tabloids. For a long time, the whereabouts of popular Lagos society lady was a matter of public concern. We can tell you for free that the mother of one now concentrates her energy in running her business, Sygnet Company Limited.